\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You are }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15143913 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What was the year of your marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 1936.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What was the year of your birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 1901.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 At Send, about six miles out from here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, I don't know, I should say, as far as I know, 3 or 4 years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And then where did you move to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 We moved to Stoughton, just outside of Guildford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How long did you stay there? Were you there a long time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Until I was about 6 or 7. And then we moved into the town.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And then you moved closer into the town?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Whereabouts was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, first I think we were in Bryant Hill which has now been ... the house has been demolished now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Bryant Hill off. Sydenham Road, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And then into Sydenham Road, South Street which is no longer
 ... now it's called Sydenham Road, the whole of it and then we moved up here in 1952, 16 or 17 years ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Which house did you live in longest before you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15143913 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ? When you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I suppose in South Street, No.30. And then when I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15143913 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 , the house next door was vacant, so we went next door, No. 31.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see, so you were in South Street...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 For about ... oh, well over 50 years. Must have been, I think. Yes, 50 years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Can you remember why your family moved from Send into Stoughton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
No, I don't know. I imagine because of my father's work. I think so. He was a farm worker and I think that's why... he got another job, you see, that way, Stoughton way. I think that was ... Stoughton was nearer his work, see. That's why he moved.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And then did he move his job again when you went to South Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. Yes, he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did he change his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, he went on the same kind of work at Stoke Park. Stoke Park Farm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I had one brother and 3 sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Where did you come in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I'm the youngest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How do they go? Who was the eldest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, my sister, eldest sister, her name was Agnes, she died about 20 years ago. Then came my brot
her. He's still alive, fortunately, he's very well, too. He's older than me, he's about 73.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How much difference was there between your eldest sister and your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, let me think. More or less 5 years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And then there would be another sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, and she's still here, fortunately, she's my only surviving sister. She's ... she's come up to 71.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see, so she was how much younger than your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 About 2 years. Yes, about 2 or 3 years, younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And then you come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, another sister. Yes, she died about 6 years or so ago. And she was only about a year older than myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And how much difference between her and her elder sister? Would it be about the same, about 2 years, or would it be longer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, I think only about a couple of years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you know how old your father was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, now, he was 90 when he died ... let me see, now. That was seven years...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Seven years ago, in 1962? So that would be 1872 he would be born and then you were born in 1901, so he was 29 when you were born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
From Sussex. 'Cos it's a Sussex name, you know, a Sussex name. Jupp, the cricketer, you know. Very well known Sussex cricketer. He was probably a distant relative of
 mine. I don't know if he was, but I did meet somebody a year to 2 ago, a lady who works in the police station in Woodbridge Road she was in the sort of lost property office there. My wife found something, she took it to the police station ... and she was
 a Miss Jupp, you see. And so she said to me ... asked me my name and I told her, 'oh', she said, 'it was my maiden name. It's a Sussex name', I said, 'I know'. You see, her people came from Sussex, too.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Whereabouts did your father come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think, I'm not quite certain. I think it was Rudgwick. My mother came from there and I think my father did, too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was he a farm labourer before he was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15143913 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, he was all his life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did he have any other job, casual or part time, apart from this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang1034\langfe1033\langnp1034\insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang1034\langfe1033\langnp1034\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no, no, no. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, because the hours in those days, you know, was 7 days a week, 168 hours a week, almost.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did he retire, or did he go on working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, he worked 'till he was about 70.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember your father ever being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I wonder if you have any idea how old your mother was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Let me see, now. She died in 1930.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And how old was she then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, 1936, I beg your pardon. 1936. She was almost ... she'd have been 68 if she'd lived another 3 months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see. We'll say that she was 68, so she would be born in 1868.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname metricconverter}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue 1868, a}}}1868, a{\*\xmlclose}
 hundred years ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, and you were born in 1901, so she would be 33. So she was a little older than your father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, she was, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You said she came from Rudgwick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you know if she had any work before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15143913 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't know. No, I couldn't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did she work after she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15143913 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ? Apart from her home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no. Well, let me think
, now. I think she used to go ... occasionally, only occasionally, to help with housework or something, but she didn't have a permanent job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would this be when you children were small, or later on?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When we were older. We were still at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 But not babies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, no. My eldest sister, the eldest of the family, well she was a few years older than me, so she was able to cope with us, you see.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see, so if your mother was out she looked after you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 She looked after us, you see. But she wasn't out every day. She used to go occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Can I ask you now something about your life at home when you were a child, the time up to when you left school. How many rooms were there in the house at South Street where you lived so long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Let me see, now. Five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Could you describe the house to me?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Let me see, now. These rooms were practically all one on top of the other, you see, there were 3 flights of stairs. The kitchen was underground, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 In the basement?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, in the basement. Very inconvenient.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Because it was on a very steep hill, wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And so you had the kitchen in the basement. Was there any other room in the basement?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, not in the basement, no, no. Let me see ... 
there was no room in the basement; there's the ... well, we used to live upstairs, ground level, you see, street level. Then there were 2 other flights of stairs and then I think there were two ... the top rooms were more or less ... a sort of an attic, y
ou know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was that used as a bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That was used as a bedroom. There were 2 on the lower floor, you see. Very small.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was that the middle one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. A very antiquated building. Those houses were about 400 years old, I believe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And so on the ground floor there was the kitchen. Was there a sitting}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149623\charrsid1126089 -}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, the sitting}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149623\charrsid1126089 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 room, I suppose, was really ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Or was there only one room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was ... yes, I suppose what we used to consider the sitting}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149623\charrsid1126089 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 room, we lived there, too, was on the first floor, you see, street level. Then stairs... 'course, it was very damp in there, in the old kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You didn't have a bathroom, I suppose?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, we didn't have a bathroom. Oh, my word, no. This is the first house I've ever lived in with a bathroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was there a lavatory outside, or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Outside, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did anyone else besides your parents and brother and sisters live in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No relatives, or lodgers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no. Oh, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your mother ever pay anyone to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was the washing done at home? Or sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, my mother did it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 It was all done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your mother or father mend or make the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, my mother used to do mending. But she didn't do any making, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were the clothes new or secondhand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, that's a good question! Some of them were secondhand. For instance, my brother, when he used to grow out of his clothes, see, I used 
to have them myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 They were passed on to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Passed on to me, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And I suppose your sisters, the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So the elder ones would have most of the new things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would they be bought at a shop in Guildford? Or through some sort of club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I think we used to get them in Guildford, but I don't know where, can't remember now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what about shoes, would the same apply?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, the same applied ... Well, I can't quite remembe
r about the shoes. Well, my brother takes the same size shoes as I do now, but whether his shoes were any good to me ... no, I don't think I ever had his shoes. I think he used to wear them out, you see, and then they were no good to me, you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So then you'd have to have new ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I'd have to have new ones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And they'd be bought in Guildford, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your father help your mother with any of the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think he did, no. As a matter of fact it w
as a question of time, really, you see, because he used to be off about 5 o'clock in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So he wouldn't be there, really to help her with the cleaning or the cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Or washing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 My mother used to do the fires, and when we got old enough, you see, we used to give a hand, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about decorating? Who did the decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, the landlord did in those days. Obviously they wouldn't now. We have to do it ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about the repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, the landlord did the repairs and the decorating.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what about any improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, if any. The landlord was responsible, but I'm afraid I don't remember any improvements.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your father ever dress or undress you? Or bath you, as children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't remember it, no, I think my mother did.
