\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think probably sometimes we used to have breakfast down in the kitchen, you know. I think so. On occasions.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 At breakfast time your father would have gone, would he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, because he used to leave at 5 o'clock, or before {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname metricconverter}
{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue 5 in}}}5 in{\*\xmlclose} the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did he manage, did he take breakfast with him, or did he come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Oh, no, he'd be gone all day. He'd take food with him, you see. He'd have a hot meal on his return in the evening. So he used to ... I think at some t
ime my mother used to get up and see him off, you know. Now latterly he looked after himself in the mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see, and got himself off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Got himself off, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would he cook something for himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, Oh, yes, he would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What members of the family would be present at breakfast? All of you except your father? Or would somebody else have gone as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 'Course, when we were all of school age, of course, we were all there together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Have you any recollection of what you usually had to eat and drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, dear. No, I haven't. We used to begin with a cereal, I know. Quaker Oats was a favourite thing in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you have a cooked breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, we used to have a cooked breakfast, always, oh, yes. Oh, yes, rather, oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Bacon or eggs or something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes, that's right, we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what did you have to drink, tea or cocoa, or...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 In the morning, tea, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have anything different on certain days, such as Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 For breakfast, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, this ... I think Mother used to ring the changes, you know. Can't remember exactly, now. It's a few years ago.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 There wouldn't be any special celebrations on Sundays for breakfast? It would be the same as other days, would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I can't quite remember, now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What happened on Sundays midday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, we'd have a slap-up meal. We did every day, as a matter of fact. We used to have a hot meal every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, in the middle of the day, every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would Sundays be special, or would it be very similar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Very similar on Sundays. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would happen in the evening, would you have tea, or would you have supper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 We used to have tea, yes, when
 we got home from school, and then when we were very young we used to be in bed by 7, so ... 'course we didn't often have ... after having our tea about half past 4, or just after 4 o'clock, there wasn't much ... you see. Still I imagine we used to have a
 hot drink and some biscuits or something, you know, before going to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When you say tea, do you mean bread and butter and jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would happen then for your father, would a meal be kept hot for him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, my mother would cook him a meal, yes. Far as I can remember he used to be home about, say about 6 o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would she cook something specially for him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 On Sundays would you have anything different? Would you have a special tea on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I think we used to have the same, you know, bread and butter, jam, cakes, so forth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would your mother bake the cakes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather. Oh, yes. Even to this day I much prefer homemade cakes to bought ones. Oh, yes, rather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And
 would the pattern for Sunday evening. ... what would happen for Sunday evening supper. Would you all have supper, or would you have just a drink before you went to bed? Would your father work on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 He used to work in the mornings sometimes. He
 didn't have to start work so early on Sunday mornings, but he'd have to go in sometime on a Sunday, for an hour or two, anyhow. But when I was about 9, yes I was about 9, I joined the choir, you see. So I used to sing in the choir at half past 6 on Sunda
y night, so I didn't get home until about 8.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 This would be Holy Trinity, would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Holy Trinity, yes. Oh, I still go there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your mother or father bake their own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did she make her own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, she used to make jam occasionally, yes, she did. Not regularly, you know. Occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did she bottle any fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think she did, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did she make pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No. No, I don't think so, because I remember when I was a yo
ung boy a shop in Sydenham Road, a little cottage as a matter of fact, they used to put certain of this stuff in the window - been pulled down, now, a few years - a man named Phillips used to own this house and he was a painter by trade, worked on his own
, you see, and his wife used to make pickles, you see, and we used to get some very cheaply and we used to go up there and get some, so there was no need for my mother to make any. Oh, beautiful pickles, too, they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 They had vegetables, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about wine, did she ever make any homemade wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did she ever make any herbal remedies for the family? Like homemade medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think she did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Any beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No. Oh, no. My mother never liked drink at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your father or mother grow any of their own vegetables? Or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 We didn't have a garden, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So they'd have to buy all of it, would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Buy all of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would your father ever get anything from Stoke Park? Would he bring back anything from his work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't know. I don't know whether there were any vegetables up there. I don't think they used to grow them up there. I don't think so.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you ever remember having tinned or dried vegetables?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't. It was all fresh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Any tinned or dried fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No. I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have any livestock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No. We had no room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How many times a week did you eat meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I suppose every day, or more or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about breakfast, if you sometimes had bacon for breakfast would you sometimes have it twice a day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, very often, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember if you ever had tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't remember. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you ever get extra meat, such a rabbit, from poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, my mother used to often buy rabbit, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That would be from the butchers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you ever remember seeing your mother have less food so that the family could have more? Do you think she ever went short?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't think so. I shouldn't like to feel that she did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You don't remember ever seeing her help herself to a smaller portion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your father have a larger portion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. I think he had an enormous appetite, working the land.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were you allowed to talk during meals when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, we weren't. When we were very small, I remember that, we weren't allowed to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked? Or did you have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Well, I think we had to have more or less what was there. I mean to say, it was not good us saying 'we don't like this sort of hash, you know', we had to eat it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What was your parents' attitude if you left some food uneaten on the plate?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Well now, let me think. Didn't go down very well with them, I don't think. If I used to say 'I didn't like that' my mother used to say 'well, you've got to eat that', you see. 'You sit down and eat that'.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Finish it up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
If there was something on the table you wanted, like the salt, could you ask someone to pass it to you or did you have to wait until it was offered to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, you could ask.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, oh, yes. Yes, we were allowed to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes, we were, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Could you bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, my word, no. Oh, no. I remember on one occasion I used to try to smuggle a newspaper and I used to get a dressing down for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When everybody else had finished, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So you had to wait until the last one had finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Normally, except for breakfast when your father had had to leave early, did all the family sit at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would your father be with you for other meals when he was home? He'd sit with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you always have the same places at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, we always had our own places. That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How was the meal served? By whom would it be served?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, normally by my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What order were you served in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, normally, I think, my father, you see, and then the eldest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Your sister, and then go downwards?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
When you were too young to feed yourself, where would you have your food, would you remember? I suppose you wouldn't. Would you sit at a hight chair, I wonder? You were the youngest, weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I was the youngest. I think I must have some time sat in a high chair. I think so, but I don't know for certain.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did she show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes. Oh, yes, Rather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 If you had any worries could you share them with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes, rather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about your father, was he easy to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, not to easy as my mother, as a matter of fact.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did he show affection, or was he undemonstrative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, no, he didn't show much affection I'm afraid, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 If you were worried would you feel like sharing your worry with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I had to naturally be respectful, and so forth, and not be cheeky.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have to be obedient?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Respectful and obedient?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your brother and sisters in certain ways, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How would you be expected to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, there again, you see, I had to treat them with respect, and if I were to start a row with them, or fighting, that sort 
of thing, especially with my brother ... I should be ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That would be disapproved of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I should be very much in the doghouse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your parents think you should hit back, or not, if another child hurt you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, they didn't expect me to hit back. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you'd grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What kind of person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you think they wanted you to consider certain things important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, my mother was a very good churchwom
an, you know, more so than my father, he didn't go to Church, not as far back as I can remember. He might have when he was a younger man. But my mother always brought us up to go to Church, you see, go to Sunday School and the ... so I joined the choir, y
ou see, as a boy, and I'm very grateful. But you see, she was a very religious person, my mother, and I owe her a lot, you see, for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What sort of things do you think she would feel would be very important? Would it be things like honesty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Good manners, courtesy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Oh, yes, rather. Yes, good manners and honesty. Yes. Yes, she believed ... she was a very good-living person and expected us ... tried to bring us up in the right way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 To be the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What did your parents think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Oh, well, they abhorred it, especially my mother, you know. She wouldn't allow us to swear. If she heard us swearing she'd be down on us, you see, you'd get a hiding for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would your father not be so particular?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, he was particular, but not as particular as my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When grownups were talking were you allowed to join in when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, we had to be very quiet and mind our p's and q's when they were talking. Oh, yes, rather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 If you did something that your parents disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 A good telling-off and a hiding. One or the other, or probably both.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Who would tell you off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, both of them, I expect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 But who would give you the hiding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, I think my mother would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would it be often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think so, I don't remember having many hidings.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would your father ever punish you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 He used to punish me, but not very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember any particular occasion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't, no. I can't think of anything in particular.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember how you felt about being punished? Do you feel that you deserved it, or that it was rather unfair in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I think I used to think it was unfair, you know, in those days, but of course now I think it was as much deserved as ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember if you and your brother and sisters grumbled at all? When you were punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, no, probably my brother would have said 'serves you jolly well right', you know, that kind of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Would you say that you received the ideas you had about how to behave from both your parents, or did one play a more important part than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think my mother did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Well, I used to get a small ... my mother couldn't afford to arrange a party for us, you know not like these days I used to get a small present from my mother, what she could afford, you see. And then, of course, I, bein
g the youngest of the family, when my brother and sisters were working, of course, they used to give me presents, too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 As soon as they were earning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When they were earning, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Before that you wouldn't have so many presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, very little at Christmas or birthdays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you have anything special to eat on your birthday? Would your mother make a special cake?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, yes. Probably ... yes, my mother used to bake a cake specially for the birthdays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you have any friends in to tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, probably one or two, but not a dozen like the children nowadays, or 20.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Can you remember anything you did with your mother and father together on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 We used to always spend Christmas Day together, but...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What did you do on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I remember from 3 years I used to go to Church on Christmas Day, in the morning.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you all go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 We all used to go. I don't know if my father went, but my mother used to take us as children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And would you have a big meal midday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes. Oh, yes, we'd have a Christmas dinner, you know. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And then would you celebrate together as a family the latter part of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have games, or things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather. Oh, yes, we used to have quite a good Christmas, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have any musical instruments in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 We used to have a gramophone. That's about all I can remember. We didn't have a piano or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was there any one in the family who sang besides yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you ever sing with the family? Did you ever have a singsong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, we used to have a singsong. Oh, yes, yes, but none of us were official singers, really. Well, I was in the choir, I won't
 say that I was on official singer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I was thinking of an informal singer, as a family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Singing carols, and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, we used to go ... my sisters and I, we used to go round carol singing, you know. Oh, yes,
 round the houses. Oh, yes, rather. We used to enjoy that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your parents play any games with you? On Christmas Day, or other occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't remember them playing games, no. No, I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were there any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Any newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Any magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think we used to have ... Yes, we used to have the occasional magazine, some we had given us, I think.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember seeing your mother or father reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. Yes. My mother wasn't a big reader, though, that was my father. But I think as children we used to read more than they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you ever remember your father or mother reading aloud to you to to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I remember my mother reading aloud to us, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember a funeral in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When you were a child, I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No. Not in the family, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were you ever taken out visiting neighbours, friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Who would you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Wel
l, my mother used to take us to an aunt, an old aunt of hers who used to live in Shalford, as a matter of fact. We used to go fairly frequently there. I used to go there to tea more than anywhere else, I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Used to walk in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you? All the way and back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, used to think nothing of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And your mother, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather. Well, we used to be walkers in our family. I had an old aunt, my mother's sister who died at the age of 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname metricconverter}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue 91 a}}}91 a{\*\xmlclose}
 few years ago and she used to walk from Cranleigh to Guildford, and back, in the same day, and think nothing of it. And I think she owed her long life to ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That was {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname metricconverter}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue 10 miles}}}10 miles
{\*\xmlclose} each way, wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname metricconverter}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue 10 miles}}}10 miles
{\*\xmlclose} each way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were you ever taken shopping in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, I used to go out shopping with my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would it always be your mother, or would you go with any one else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, I'd go with my sisters, too. I used to look forward to going round and looking in the
 shops at Christmas time, though, when I was a small boy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you ever go out with just your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Yes, yes, my brother and I used to go out, you know. Sometimes we used to go up to the farm, you see, and ... We all of us did, once upon a time, occasionally.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Can you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days? I think you said that you helped your mother with cleaning the knives and doing errands, would that be on Saturday mornings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, Saturdays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would you do in the afternoons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, dear, oh, dear ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you be free to do what you liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I probably went out walking Saturday afternoons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you go out with your brother and sisters, or with friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I used to ... I used to go to choir 
boy things, I think, too. I remember one Saturday a good many years ago one of our curates took, oh, about half a dozen choirboys from Trinity out to Blackheath. Do you know the priory Church there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I do. Did you walk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I remember going there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you walk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Walked all the way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, and we had tea, I think at Chilworth, and we walked back from there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about Sundays? What would you do on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 On Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I used to spend quite a time at the Church on Sundays, especially after I joined the choir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Sunday mornings you would go to Church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, used to go to Sunday School, then ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, in those days we used to have the Sunday School in the day school, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would that be in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
In the morning, from 10 until ... or quarter to 10 'till about 10 to 11 and then we used to go to Church, you see. And then in the afternoon we'd go to the children's service at 3 o'clock, and then to evensong at half past 6.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 At the children's service would you be singing in the choir or going as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I used to sing in the choir in the afternoon, too.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see, so you'd be singing in the choir 3 times on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, and sometimes 4 times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have different clothes to wear on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather. Oh, yes, we used to wear our Sunday suit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you ever play games on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No. No, I wasn't allowed to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Your parents thought it wrong to play on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would they think it wrong to work on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Well, my father was so often sent to work on a Sunday, very often, but my mother wasn't keen on the idea. As a matter of fact I've always been against Sunday work 
myself. Of course, my work in the Church isn't typical, it wasn't work, I mean to say. In any case I go to Church on a Sunday, but I wouldn't do any work outside the Church on a Sunday, I never have done. Against my principle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think you said your mother used to go to Church on Sundays, but your father only infrequently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And you've told me how often you went, and you went to Sunday School. Were there any Sunday School outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would they be like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Well, in the summertime we used to have ... not an outing to the seaside like they do now, we used to have our Sunday School treat in Shalford Park. Used to have games there, you know, but we used to thoroughly enjoy it. I think we had a coach to take
 us to Shalford Park, and to bring us back. We used to play games there and have tea there. A very good afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Sort of sports, I suppose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Sports, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What other social activities were organi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149623\charrsid1126089 z}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ed by the Church? That you took part in. Did the choir have any special activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, the choir ... we used to have an outing to the ... those outings were to the sea. You know, seaside. And they still do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would that be once a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Once a year, yes. And then after I left the choir they used to have an extra treat, I don't know ... }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid149623\charrsid1126089 in}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089  ... recent years, I don't think they still do now, but once upon a time they used to go to the theatre, a pantomime, you know, in January.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So they'd have an outing in the summer and one in the winter?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 One in the wintertime, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you be paid in the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Yes. Oh, yes. Yes, we used to get about ... I used to sing in the ... at Evensong every night, six weeknights as well as Sundays, at half past 5 we used to have a said ... well, partly said and partly sung Evensong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Every weekday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Oh, yes, when I joined the choir, I joined in 1910, and we used to sing ... from about 9, 10 or 11 I started this daily choir, in the daily choir, we used to sing a hymn and say the psa
lms, alternate verses with the priest, you see, and we used to sing the Magnificat and the Nunc Dimitis, and the service used to last half an hour. Well, for that we used to get 6/6 a quarter, which was a lot of money in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And were you allowed to keep it, or did you give it to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Oh, I gave ... yes, I was allowed to keep some of it, but not very much. And we used to get paid for choir practices. But we never got paid for Sundays. I remember the old choirmaster saying 'you must
n't expect to get paid on Sundays. You should come to Church on Sundays and not expect to be paid'.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 But you were paid for weekdays, and for practice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, and we got paid for weddings and for funerals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did the Church run any temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Yes, the old Church of England Temperance Society which has now, I think, ceased to exist in every part of the country. I haven't heard anything or read anything about the society for years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were you ever a member of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I joined th
e C.T.S., oh, when I was about 16, I think. I was on the committee, as a matter of fact, in this parish. It's some years ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you belong to any other club organi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149623\charrsid1126089 z}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ed by the Church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, the Communicants Guild Club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What did you do in that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Oh, we used to play games in the parish hall, you know, billiards, those who liked billiards; and other games, ping-pong, and so forth. And we used to have a service in Church occasionally, I think, the members. But that closed ... ceased to exist
 years ago. Maybe other things have taken their place, of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was Grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No. No, I'm afraid not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. Yes, we were, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think we ever had family prayers but we used to say ... we were taught to say our own prayers, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you know if your father took an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, he didn't. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 If he had done, what sort of attitude do you think he would have taken? Where would his sympathies lie?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I don't know. I should think probably the Liberal Party.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think so. But he wasn't really very interested, in politics at all, as far as I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your mother take any interest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you think she would have felt the same as your father? Or do you think she would have had different views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That I can't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you think your father might have been interested in the Liberal Party for any particular reason?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't know. I think probably he thought for the working man, that the Liberal Party was the party, for the working man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 To improve the conditions, this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember your father or mother voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, I remember him voting, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You don't know what they voted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 They never told you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't remember if they ever did tell me. I certainly don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 In some places at that time men felt that they risked losing their employment if they voted differently from their employers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, that's right, I remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you think your father ever felt like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't think so. I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was your father ever a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And you don't remember him working for one of the parties at an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Or your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your parents take part in any political activity other than at election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I think my mother was very fully occupied with the affairs of the home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was she always working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Always working, you see. As I said my father, his job was a very fulltime job so neither of them had very much leisure time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Very little, I'm afraid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Very, very rarely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 If she did go, would she go with a friend, or would she go to see relations or what would she do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, if she did go, and that was only on very rare occasions, she'd go to see one of her sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think you said your father got home from work about 6, as far as you remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would he do in the evenings? After he'd had his meal? Would he spend the evenings at home, or would he go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, most evenings he would spend at home. Sometimes he went out, but
 ... of course, he used to go to bed very early because he had to be up about 4 o'clock in the morning, or soon after, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did he go to any clubs or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No. I think he probably used to go to a pub occasionally, but I don't think he joined any club. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 From what you remember you don't think he went regularly to any club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No. No, he didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And your mother would never go out to anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, she never went out in the evening, no. Never, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your father ever take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did he ever attend the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Or bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no, no. He wasn't a betting man, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs? Like a boot club, or a sick club, or a funeral club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I believe my father did. I don't know whether ... and I think my mother did. Yes, they both did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was this an insurance, really, for the family and themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You don't know what sort of club it would be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 My father, I think, belonged to the ... either the Odd fellows or the Foresters Club. They are both very old clubs, aren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. What about your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think she belonged to something like that, I can't say ... I can't remember what it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did you get on with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, very well. Very well. Yes, I think we all got on very well together, really, on the whole.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was there one you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I suppose, if I were closer to one in particular more than to the others it'd probably be my youngest sister who died 6 years ago.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That would be the one next to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 The one next to me, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 As a child did you play with her mainly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, we used to play together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you play with your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. I think we all used to play together, you know, more or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have some neighbours' children that you'd play with, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes, there were 2 or 3
 girls, and boys as a matter of fact, living quite near us in South Street, you know, we were very friendly with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Whereabouts would you play, because you hadn't a garden, had you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No. We used to come sometimes on the downs, here, and play.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you ever play in the street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Yes, we used to play in the street quite a bit because in those days there was hardly any traffic about. You couldn't do it now. We often used to come up on the downs though, especially in the summertime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you ever play in other children's homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did they come into your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. Oh, yes, rather, yes. My sisters often used to bring their friends in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You don't remember any of the games you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, I don't now, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would you play on the downs? Cricket, or rounders or ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, we used to play rounders. I used to play cricket and football with my boy friends, you know, choir boy friends, and so forth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You didn't get ticked off if you were dirty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no. No, I don't think we used to get ticked off very much. My mother used to take it as a matter of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were you free to play with anyone you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, more or less, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your parents discourage you from playing with certain children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, because she knew the children we played with, you see. We'd bring them home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would there be some children that she wouldn't be very keen that you played with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. She was particular, you know, in that respect, who we played with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what do you think would be her reason for not wanting you to play with a certain child? Would it be that they were a rough family?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Rough, and if they used to used bad language and that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see, and not behave properly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Not behave properly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So that they would be a bad influence on you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You think that was the reason?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, I think that was the reason, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you belong to any youth organizations, apart from the Church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no. 'Cos in those days there weren't many youth organizations.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Scouts, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I never joined the scouts. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did you spend your free t
ime when you were at school? Did you have any hobbies? You told me that you went to ... first of all you went to Evensong every night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That was every night, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And then you'd shop for the old lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. And then, of course, apart from the services there were choir practices, you see. We used to have about 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname metricconverter}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue 4 a}}}4 a{\*\xmlclose}
 week at 6 o'clock. We used to practice, I think, at 6 o'clock on Tuesdays, Wednesdays and Fridays, and on Thursdays at 8 o'clock. So we had a pretty full week, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So this was your main interest, apart from sport.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, that's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you keep any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, we used to have a cat. We had one or two cats. My mother was fond of cats. But we never kept any birds. We never kept a dog.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you collect anything as a boy? Like stamps, or birds' eggs, or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
No, I don't think I had ... my brother used to collect birds' eggs, I think. Don't think I did. What we used to do ... be fond of, my brother and I, was collecting cigarette pictures, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I remember those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You remember those? Oh, we used to have several sets between us, my brother and I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And then did you swap them with friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you ever do any gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, because we had no garden in those days, you see. Now I make up for it, as a matter of fact.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You said you went for walks, did you ever go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think I did go. Oh, yes, for a time, but I gave it up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Where would you fish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 In the W}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7356014\charrsid1126089 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
y. I used to go with a boy who lived in the same street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would you catch? Or did you catch anything?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 We didn't used to catch much, I don't think. But I didn't continue it for very long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you ever do any bicycling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I didn't do any bicycling, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you take part in any sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I used to play with the choir, you know, cricket and stuff on the downs; and football, but apart from that, not much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember going to any theatres as a child? Or concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. I remember going to the Theatre Royal here, oh, about almost the first performance they had there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You don't know what it was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think, if it was not the first performance, it was the second or third. Yes, and it was called 'B}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7356014\charrsid1126089 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 unty Pulls The Strings', I remember that very well. O forget what year it was, but it was years ago, now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You mean it was the first time the theatre was opened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, after it was opened, yes. It was in North Street. It's been many years ago, I just don't remember the year it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you enjoy it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
I did, yes. I used to go there pretty frequently when I ... once upon a time. In the last few years it was there I used to go fairly frequently.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about concerts when you were a boy, were there any concerts in Guildford that you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, there were concerts. I remember going to ... I remember going to some in the old Barn Hall, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would the Church organi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7356014\charrsid1126089 z}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 e any concerts sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think some of those I went to were organized by the Church. Some were in our parish hall, of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about music hall?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I've never been to any music halls, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were there any cinemas here in Guildford while you were still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather. The oldest one, of course, was ..
. it's still there, the building is still there, it's been closed as a cinema for years, The Plaza now they call it, I think, Onslow Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you ever go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, I used to go there when I was a boy. Not once a week, but perhaps once in two or 3 weeks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Fairly regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And how did you pay for your ticket? Would it be out of the money that you'd earned in the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Choir practice, yes, and choir, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your parents give you any pocket money, apart from this money you earned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, I think they did, I've forgotten ... I think they did, just a very, very little, you know. Very little.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember what you spent it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Mostly on sweets, I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did anyone outside the home help your mother look after her house or family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, any relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Not that I remember, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Or friends or neighbours come and help her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 If your mother was ill or confined to bed how would she manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Well, I remember when I was about 9 my mother was in the County Hospital for about a month, but my eldest sister looked after us. And my aunt - the one I was telling you about who lived at Cranleigh - I think she came up, you know, occasionally, and helpe
d.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did she stay in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
No, I think she used to come up for the day, you know, and go back, you see. My eldest sister did most of the looking after us then. I was about 9 then, I remember that. But I think that was the only illness I remem
ber my mother having, except the last illness when she died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So your sister would do the cooking, would she, and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes. She used to do quite a bit of cooking, my eldest sister. She was very fond of baking cakes, and so forth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would she do that for your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your father have any relatives living nearby? Your mother had this aunt at Cranleigh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I think my father's relatives were all dead. Died years before, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about your mother, did she have any other relatives apart from this aunt living around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, she did have, but they died before she did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When you were a child would you see them and visit them?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes. Yes, there was the one I was speaking to yo
u about, lived at Shalford. I think she was my mother's eldest sister. She died some years before my mother. And another one I had lived at Albury, or round that way, she died some years before my mother did. And she just had this one surviving sister who
 died at about the age of 91 just a few years ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 This was the one that walked to Cranleigh?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, she was a great walker.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would your mother see her relatives regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, fairly regularly. Yes, yes. Especially the old soul from Cra
nleigh, 'cos she used to come up ... she used to like walking, you know, to come up. She used to go sometimes to see her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And would your mother walk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How would she go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, she would go by bus or by train. But she was a great walker in her younger days, my mother was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Your mother, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, because she used to walk to school, I think it was about 3 or {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname metricconverter}
{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue 4 miles}}}4 miles{\*\xmlclose} she had to walk to school when she was a girl. No buses in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your parents have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Where would they see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, my mother's friends very often used to come and see her, you know. She had a few friends in Guildford. Well, several friends.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did they share the same friends? Your mother and father, or would they have different friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I think they were really different friends, you know, mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would your mother meet her friends, say, at Church, at Holy Trinity, or how would she get to know them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think she met some at the Church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would some be neighbours who were also friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. And some old neighbours, you know, of bygone days would visit her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What? Neighbours who'd moved away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, who'd moved away, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would your father have friends that he would visit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes. He used to have friends that used to ... who he knew when we lived at Send, you see, for instance, and other places.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would he go over and see them at Send?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 He'd go over and see them, yes. And he had friends in
 Sussex, too. He used to go and see them when he could, though that wasn't very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would they come over and see them at your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes, occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were friends ever invited into the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And would they be offered anything to eat of drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would this be on a particular day or occasion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Not on any particular day, I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 If the friends were invited into the house, would they usually be your mother's friends or your father's friends? Or both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Both, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did friends ever call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, on occasions, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what about neighbours, would they come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 In without an invitation, just call in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes. Oh, yes, we had some very good neighbours, down South Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would your parents ever go out together to see friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements. What do you thi
nk your parents did when they got together with their friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't know, it's mostly talking, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did they play cards, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 They wouldn't have any music together, or something of this sort?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Many people divide society into different social groups. In that time before 1918 did you think of some people belonging to some group and some to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't know the answer to that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 For instance, would you ... if you think
 about the ... you talked about the vicar of the Church, what sort of social group would you think of him belonging to in those days?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What sort of social group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, different to now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes. For instance, when I
 was a boy and young man at Holy Trinity, we always used to get ... if the rector wanted a curate he'd always get an Oxford or Cambridge graduate.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, but before he died, this rector, he did have men who were not graduates of Oxfor
d of Cambridge. I remember the very first one to break away from tradition was an A.K.C., King's College, London, you see. But you see, now times have changed. Now you get men who are not even university men, you see, with no degree at all. Which I think 
i
s better, myself, because I don't think ... in the old days, you know, it was thought by a good many people that only men from the upper classes ought to be ordained, which was entirely wrong, because God is no respecter of persons. The first disciples we
r
e men who were in the eyes of the world would be called ignorant men, you see. But they turned the world upside down, didn't they. You see, I'm afraid that was a tendency in the old days, you know, say 50 years ago and since, you know, to have men ... to 
o
nly have men from the upper classes to be priests. Of course, all that is done away with now. With all due respect to the clergy of the past, because the rector who I'm thinking of now was in my opinion the best ... he himself was the best type of priest,
 I think. But as I say, it was the tendency in those days to get men from the ... who'd been to one of the ... one or other of the two universities, Oxford or Cambridge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Who else would be considered in those days to be in the upper classes? They wouldn
't all be graduates, would they? I mean there's be women, for instance, who wouldn't have been to the university. What families would come into that category?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What? As regards women, do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I was thinking what about doctors and people like that, would they be thought of as upper class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Doctors probably would've done. You know, I've been told, I don't know whether it's true or not, but I hope it's not true, but I've some suspicion that it is probably true, that men who failed in
 the exams for the medical profession thought 'well, I must take a profession', you see, 'I've failed, I'll be ordained', you see, which is the wrong thing. But that idea seemed to be prevalent once upon a time, I believe, that they must take a profession
,
 you see. And I think myself that the ministry should be looked on as a profession, and it often is, but it's a vocation and therefore it appeals ... it should appeal to all men, it doesn't matter whether the man concerned is a dustman or a duke, you see.
 
I mean to say, in the sight of God they're the same. And I mean to say a dustman can make as good a priest as a duke, you see. But I think in the old days it seems to be to be ... and a lot of people say it, too, I think it was rather a fact that in the o
l
d days they used to go ... if a man wanted to be ... to go into the army, you see, and he was no good at it, you see, he'd come out and he'd be ordained, you see. If he had no money, you see. If he had money he could pay for his training, you see, and he 
used to be accepted. I think that's the wrong idea.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was class very important in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, I think so. I think it was. I think it was very important in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were there sharp divisions then between one class and another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I 
think so. You see, because you were saying just now, I think, that ... about the old days that workmen were ... if they were known to vote in the opposite direction to what the employer did, he was liable to get dismissed from his job. But the point is ..
. Yes, there's a lot of truth in that, because I've been told that, but how did the employers find out how they voted, because it's supposed to be a secret ballot. Well, it is, but how did they find out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well I suppose one would presume they couldn't f
ind out exactly how they voted if they weren't told by the man himself, but they might have a hunch what his views were, mightn't they, without his actually saying how he voted, I suppose. So in Guildford in those days, what sort of people would be in the
 congregation in Holy Trinity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Well, before 1914 War, as you probably know, practically every tradesman in the High Street used to live over his shop and half the High Street is in Trinity parish, and a part is in St. Mary's parish, and a part is in S
t. Nicholas parish. Well, you see, now about half is in Trinity parish, well those tradesmen who lived there, they used to come to Trinity, you see. It was a very nice thing to go to Church on a Sunday, you see, and they used to get the Church full years 
ago. And then the 1914 War changed that, because after the War finished there was an exodus of people moving from the High Street into ... away from the town, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What, into residential areas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Residential areas, you see. But now I don't supp
ose there's one ... or hardly one shop owner in the High Street who lives over his business, over the shop. I don't know anybody now, at all, who lives over the premises.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So these shopkeepers who had businesses in the High Street would come to Holy Trinity Church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
And then would there be a cross-section of people there, too? I mean would there be some really very well-to-do- people like gentry, and so on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, you'd got doctors there, and so forth; tradesmen, and ... of course, tradesmen had money, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And would there be some poorer people, as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So it would cover, really, different groups in the town?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, that's true. Now, you see, I don't say that it happened in Holy Trinity but 
I do know that it happened in many churches up and down the country in the old days, that in churches where they had the gallery, that the working class people used to go up in the gallery, you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Because they had pew rents, didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Yes. Oh, we had pew rents at Trinity since I became a verger, because I used to send out these notices to remind the pew renters that their pew rent was due, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And if the people went up into the gallery would there be any pew rents up there, or would it be free?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, all free.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So that was probably the reason?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Yes. We used to have, in the porch at Trinity 'all seats free 5 minutes before the service'. Now, you see, somebody who paid a guinea or two gu
ineas a year, you see, came in a 5 to 11 or after 5 to 11 and saw somebody sitting in their ... they couldn't say anything then, you see, because they were too late, you had to get there before. But I think it's an awful thing. But we abolished that some 
years ago. I'm glad we did. But they used to have to do it in the old days to get a certain amount of income, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What sort of group would you say that your family belonged to? In these social groupings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 My family? Oh, I should say working class, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
And what sort of people belonged to the same group? Your father was a farm labourer, the other people living near to you what would their occupations be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, they'd be in the same group, the working class group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, and what would they do? What would their jobs be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Well, I remember there was one man who lived quite near us, he was a compositor, I think, with the Surrey Advertiser. And there was another man who worked for Southampton Brewery, firing; another man worke
d at a bakery; another man that I was telling you about just now, he was a painter and decorator.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, the one that had the shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Had the shop, yes. All various jobs but they were all, you see, in the same group.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What sort of people bel
onged to the group that the clergy would be in, because you were describing them as mainly upper class, well educated people, in those days, so they must have had money, mustn't they, to have paid for this university education, which everybody had to buy?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Who else would belong to that group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I should say lawyers, doctors, of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about bank managers and people like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, bank managers, certainly.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about teachers, how were they regarded?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I'm not quite certain about teachers. I should think probably there was a mixture, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about the headmaster of the grammar school, would he be...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Ah, well, you see, he'd be a university man. Because I think all staff of th
e grammar school here are university men, I think the whole staff are. You see, in the old days there was a ... for instance, at Holy Trinity School we had a master of arts from Oxford, a Mr. Welford. He came to Trinity School just before I left there. Ve
ry nice man. He was the only, the one and only, I think, university man on the staff there, you see. He was headmaster. I think there was a mixture there, you see, you get the upper classes and the middleclass men as schoolteachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So the middle class, would they be a stage below the clergy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That's right, and lawyers and bank managers and doctors. At least, that's what I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were you ever told to touch your cap, or show respect in some way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, I was always taught to raise my cap.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And who would you raise it to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 To a lady.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Always to a lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, and also to a schoolmaster or rector, or one of the clergy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was there anyone that you called 'sir', or 'master' or 'madam'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Oh, yes, rather! I called the rector and the clergy 'sir', and also the schoolmaster. Also my employer, naturally, I remember when I left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And who would you call 'madam'? Would you call any lady 'madam', or would you call her 'Mrs. So-and-so'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, if I met ... a lady who was a stranger to me and I didn't know her name I would address her as 'madam'.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And it was only if you knew them that you would call them 'Mrs. So-and-so'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents in these ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Ah, yes, I remember them addressing my mother as 'madam', and, of course, raising hats to her in the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 In the South Street area who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, I don't know, difficult to say. I should imagine they were all as important as the other.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 They were all about the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think so, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about Holy Trinity parish, who would be the most important people in that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
In the parish? Of course, the parish comprises several roads and streets. That's right up here and down to the ... as far as the bottom of the ... halfway down the High Street ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I suppose the rector would be considered quite important, would he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, he would ... Oh, yes, well, he would be ... Well, to my mind he would be the most important man in the parish. The most important.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about the shopkeepers, would they be very important, or would there be other people who would be considered superior?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, I should think so. I should think if the mayor lived in the parish he would be considered a very important person.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would there be any gentry living in the parish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Oh, yes. Yes, because, you see, Epsom Road ... well, Epsom Road is in this parish; London Road, and Southfield, but not -? to - Shalford, your parish. Southfield, Castle Hill, where canon \{ILLEGIBLE\} my rector, lives.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about farmers? How were they regarded in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
I don't know, I'm sure. I should imagine in those days there was a mixture of class, between middle class and upper class, I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You mean there were tenant farmers and farmers who were sort of county gentry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what about employers? I suppose people like Dennis's factory would exist in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, Dennis's have been in existence for years and years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would the head people at Dennis's be considered important in Guildford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I should image so. I should imagine so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I suppose there were one or two other factories in Guildford, as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. 'Course, Dennis's, they started in a very small way. I'm told that Sir Raymond Dennis ... I think it was the late Sir Ray
mond Dennis who started the shop, started the business ... he started with only a small sample shop there, you know. Yes, and of course, that firm has been in existence for many years, so it would be considered an important firm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What sort of people would you say went to Church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 In those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, trades people, a lot of them. I should think a great number of trades people, from the shops in the town, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would there be any difference in the people that went to the Chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, 'cos a good many gentry I think are, or were, non-conformists, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about Roman Catholics? Were there any Roman Catholics in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't know. Not so many, I don't think, but of course, they've grown. They've 
got a good following now, they're opening new Churches. They're always the first on new building sites, the Roman Catholic churches.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When we were talking last week about the most important people in the parish and the sort of people who form the congr
egation of Holy Trinity in the days when you were a youngster; do you remember if you came into contact with any of these people you were referring to? You did, of course, come into contact with the rector and the curate. Would you come into contact with 
doctors or lawyers or bank managers, or anybody like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I didn't come into contact with them, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Not personally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Why did you think that in the community they were felt to be important? What would be the reason?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I suppose because of their position.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And would that be a result of having more money, or being in a different social strata, or training?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I think it would be because of their social position, and also because of their money, you know. I think 
that was the attitude in the old days. I think money...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was important, was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Was important. I won't say altogether. I mean to say in a church ... although it's quite possible in those days that even in a church people who had money were looked
 upon, you know, as important people. I suppose because the church was dependent on those people for money to keep the church going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think that when we mentioned Roman Catholics last time you said you felt there weren't very many Roman Catholics in 
Guildford at that period. Was there any friction between Roman Catholics and the other church-going people in the town?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't know that there was any friction, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You weren't aware of any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I wasn't aware of any, no. But I suppos
e ... well, I suppose even today Although the Church ... of course, you can't ... it's difficult to tell today, because there's not the amount of church-going there was then in the old days, naturally, but in St. Joseph's, the Roman Catholic Church, they'
v
e had a new wing put on on that Church a few years ago. A friend of mine told me they could now do with even a bigger church, because they get such big congregations. But of course, they are the only Roman Catholic Church in the town, you see, in the town
 itself. But I think that's a good sign. I often wish we could get a few more people in our church.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 But you don't remember any friction?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, not any friction, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When you lived in South Street did all the people in the working class group 
have the same standard of living? Or would you say that there were different groups within it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think there were different groups. Some of them were very poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Can you think of a family that was very poor? What would be the occupation of t
he breadwinner? Was there any particular reason why they were poor; would it be that they ... perhaps somebody in the family spent too much on drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think that was one cause. Yes, I think one or two men in our area were builders' labourers, y
ou know, and there was a public house in South Street which has been demolished now, just a few years ago, you remember it, do you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I do remember it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 The King's Head. Of course, that ceased to be a public house, oh a good many years ago, no
w, but when I was a boy I remember it. Can't remember the landlord's name, but quite of few of these men did frequent the place, and I think more than one spent too much money on drink. Of course, it kept them very poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And I suppose, too, thinking of builders' labourers this would depend, particular in the winter, on weather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And there wouldn't be any unemployment pay, would there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, not in those days, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So that if you weren't working you weren't earning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You weren't earning. And then, of course, in the wintertime the weather was too bad, of course, they couldn't work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you think, then, that there would be more than two groups, a group like yourself where your father had regular work, didn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Which was prudently ... money was prudently used; and a group where the work might be spasmodic, and perhaps they might spend too much on drink. Would there be any other groups in addition to this? Would there be some people who had more money still?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, oh, yes, I think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Than your family, for instance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, definitely.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what would this be due to, what would they do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, there was one man in our street who was a compositor on a newspaper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see, so did that mean that he would earn a better income?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, he had a better income, oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So that would be a different group, again, within the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you think that one of these groups would feel itself superior to the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Well, now ... No, I don't think so. For instance, there was a man who lived opposite us in South Street who was a foreman - suppose they call them foreman, or superintendent - of the waterworks in Mill Mead, and ... as a matter of fact the 
house is still there, and it's just at the bottom of Pewley Hill - and he was very nice, a nice family, too, and I don't think that they considered themselves superior to us, they seemed to be very friendly, you know. No, I don't think there was anything 
like that about them. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would your family consider themselves superior to the ... say, the labourers, the builders' labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember if some families were thought of as 'rough' and some as 'respectable'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, some were. Some we thought of as 'rough'.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would the reason be for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I suppose because they used to drink, and so forth. Even the wives, I'm afraid, too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would there be a distinction of this kind between crafts
men and labourers? Would the labourers be thought of as rough, or not necessarily so?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Not necessarily, no, no. No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was it, then, more the way they lived than what they were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, more, I think, in the way they lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would the children, perhaps, behave differently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. I think, perhaps, some of the children were inclined to be a bit ... you know, they felt themselves to be a bit superior, you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, the children, but not the parents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your mother and father behave in the same way to people in different social groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes. Oh, yes, I think they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social group?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 If she'd been asked, what social group do you think she would have said she belonged to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Now, let me think. I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You said that you think that your family was a working class family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Now, would she have felt the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, I think she would have done. Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Could this be because she was thinking of her parents and the life she'd had with them, or would it be because of your father's work, or the house she lived in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I think it was because ... you know, of her general background, you see. Her parents were working class people, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15143913 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
 a working class man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was it possible at that time to move from one group in a social class to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was it possible?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. Do you know anyone who did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
No, I can't think of anybody in particular. I suppose it was possible. I suppose if a man changed his job, you see ... For instance, if my father could have done, and if he did change his job ... if he had changed hi
s job, I mean to say, given a different type of work, you see, he could consider himself \{BLANK\} in a different group.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So this would depend, really, on getting a different job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Different job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Which would put you in a different situation socially?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, oh, yes. Definitely, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember anyone being described as 'a real gentleman' or a 'real lady'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Why do you think that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I think when I was a boy that we looked upon people who were socially in 
the upper ten, shall I say, as 'ladies' and 'gentlemen', I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Yes, I think so. Although, of course, it's possible to be a lady or a gentleman when you haven't got a thing in the world. I mean to say, it shows you how you think, of c
ourse, when you get older. I used to look upon people who had money, you know, and a good social position, and that, as the superior people, ladies and gentlemen, you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And you would call such a woman 'a real lady'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. Because of the sort of house they lived in and they had money, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And their social position?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Social position.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I was never afraid of the police at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You weren't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, my word no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you know one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Oh, yes, I mean to say, we used to get to know them because, you see, they were frequently up our way. You used to see more policeman in those days in the street than you do now. Oh, yes, rather. I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When you were naughty, as a child, did your mother ever day 'I'll call a policeman'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, I think she did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 But you weren't afraid of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did they treat the people in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 The police?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, dear, I don't know. I can't remember. I don't think they were rough with them. I think they were friendly, on the whole.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You don't remember any incident when they were rough or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you see anything of your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, rather, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What did you feel about him as a landlord?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, he was quite good. Quite a good landlord.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes. Oh, yes, I knew him very well, as a matter of fact. He was our landlord for a good number of years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your parents know him at the time when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 They knew him quite well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember feeling that your parents had a struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Yes. It wasn't all roses, you know. I think it was as much as they could do to make ends meet. I think they just did manage to make ends meet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 As a child do you remember if this worried you? or what you felt about it? Were you conscious of it and were you ever anxious?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
I was conscious of it when I got old enough, you know, to realize. As for being anxious or not, I can't remember. I think, by the time I left school I was a bit anxious, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You were becoming a bit more aware of their difficulties, I suppose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think I did ask you before. Your father wasn't ever out of work, was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I never remember him being out of work at all, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was he ill at any time, and unable to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
I never knew him to be ill, as a matter of fact. No, perhaps he would be away from work for a day or two with a cold or something like that, but I don't remember that he had any serious illness. A very healthy man, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you ever get any help, as a family, from the Guardians, or the Parish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Or any charity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, not that I remember, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When there was someone in the district whom the people disapproved of very strongly was there any special way in which they showed it?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, excepting in this way they would probably ignore them, you know, if they met them out in the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see, this would be, really, sent to Coventry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 But they wouldn't take any active action against them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, I don't think so.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 In fact they wouldn't make them so unhappy that they had to move away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Can we think a little bit about your time at school. Did you have any lessons from your parents before you went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Where did you go to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, first of all I went to Stoughton School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I was living there, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How old would you be then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I suppose, about 5.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would that be a Board School, or a Church school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That was a Board school, Stoughton, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was it mixed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, it was mixed, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When you first started can you remember at all what time you started in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think it was about 9 o'clock. Yes, it was 9 o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you come back to lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, because I think we lived near the school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What time would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 12 o'clock, I think, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And you'd go back again, would you, in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 At 2 o'clock, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Even at the age of 5?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, a full day. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What time would afternoon school finish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 About half past 3, or 4.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 We used to walk because we lived near, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How long would it take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, I think only 5 to 10 minutes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did anyone go with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think my eldest sister used to take me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What did you think of school, do you remember? That school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I wasn't very keen. It seems ... so my parents have told me since, not when I first started.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You didn't like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, not when I first started. In time I got used to it, you know, and liked it better.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember how you felt about the teachers? Do you remember the teachers at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Not in those days, no, not when I was 5.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did them emphasi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7356014\charrsid1126089 z}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 e certain things as important in life? Such as manners and tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes. Yes, yes, I'm sure they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about ways of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think that, too, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 If you did something the teachers disapproved of, what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I think you got punished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You can't remember what sort of punishment, when you were very small?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I think one punishment was they used to set us to stand in a corner. And I think in those days they used to blindfold us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And stand you in the corner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did they treat the boys and the girls the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Just the same, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What sort of reason would you be punished for? What would you have done to deserve that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Probably through talking. I used to get punished when I was older for that, talking in class. My secret vice, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would lateness be considered something that had to be punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. You'd bet punished for being late, anyhow, if you were late more than once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Disobedience?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Supposing your work wasn't very good?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, if your work wasn't very good ... I can't remember now when I was very small about that,
 but later on if your work wasn't very good, well you'd stay in after school and do so many lines, about 500 lines, you know, that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your parents show an interest in your school work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, I think they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did they ever ask you what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 In those days would they visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't remember my parents ever visiting the school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would they meet the teachers at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't remember them meeting them, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did the other children in the Stoughton School come from similar types of home to your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. Yes, they did. Quite a number of them, anyhow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, when I was older, older than 5, I used to think they did. Probably it was just my feeling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Why did you think they did, do you remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, for instance, if we misbehaved ourselves, you see, sometimes we used to think 'oh, well, we'll have to
 stay in afterwards', another child would probably do the same thing and get away with it, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see, and you felt that was rather unfair as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 We felt it was rather unfair, and that there was a certain amount of favouritism, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That they'd got a down on you, for some reason?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes. It was probably only imagination, but that's how I felt.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were there any gangs or groups in that school, do you remember? Little groups that stuck together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think there 
were. And I found that, I think, when I was older, too. A certain number of gangs, you know, that used to keep themselves to themselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were there any children who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think sometimes there probably were children, ju
st here and there, you know, who wanted to keep themselves to themselves and were very reluctant to join in games with other children, and so forth.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you remember at all why what was? Was it because they were very shy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, I think probably ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Or they didn't feel accepted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think a lot of it was due to shyness.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would it be because they had a particular background?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, probably. It might have been the case of an only child ... being an only child, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Or I wondered if they came from some institution or something like that instead of an ordinary home. Would that make any difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, probably, they might have come from homes. I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Now, you went on to another school after that, didn't you, that was Holy Trinity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, Charlotte}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7356014\charrsid1126089 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ville School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That was a Board School, was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And was that mixed, as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Mixed, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How old would you be when you went there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, let me see now. I suppose I was about 8 or 9, when we went to Charlotte}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3938720\charrsid1126089 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ville. I was only there for about a year or two when I went to Trinity School and I stayed there for the best of my school days..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Can we just go very briefly through your period at Charlotte}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3938720\charrsid1126089 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ville, then we'll go on to Holy Trinity. You were 9 when you went: would you go to school all day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And go home to lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would the hours be very similar to Stoughton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Very similar to Stoughton, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And it was a mixed Board school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You'd walk to it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And that would be very near home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 It would only take you a few minutes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, from South Street up there, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 At that time would you go by yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. Well, we all went ... except my eldest sister, she'd left then. Four of us went there together, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 But you wouldn't be taken to school by anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did you like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I liked it, I think, at first, bu
t then after a year or two I wasn't so keen on it. Some of my friends were attending Holy Trinity School and I was joining the Holy Trinity choir ... or I had joined the Holy Trinity choir, and I thought it would be rather nice to go to the school, you se
e. That was why I left. It was the Church school, you see. That was the reason I left. And then, of course, it was easy ... you could leave at will, then, to go to another school. Oh, yes, rather, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about the teachers at Charlotte}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3938720\charrsid1126089 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ville School, do you remember anything about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I remember the headmaster, he was very, very severe. Oh, yes, very severe indeed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were you frightened of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I think I was. Some of the boys were, and some of the girls were because he was
 notoriously ... well, shall I say in some cases we thought we was rather cruel, as a matter of fact.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Why would that be, because of his punishments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Because of his severe punishments, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What sort of severe punishment? Do you mean caning, or something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Caning, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And would that be very frequent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes. He caned somebody, I think, every day, you know. At least one or 2 every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would that be for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I suppose today we would call the 
things trivial, but they certainly weren't trivial to him. Well, we used to think he'd cane anybody, really, you know, just for the sake of caning, at the slightest provocation. For instance, if you were late for school, or, I think, if you came to school
 with dirty shoes on, and that sort of thing, you'd get caned for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes. He was very strict, this headmaster.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what about the girls, would they be treated the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 They were caned, too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes,
 rather, yes. Yes, I can remember that now. I can remember a girl who was caned, and she had rather a violent temper, this girl, and the headmaster hurt her so much that she picked up the cane afterwards and snapped it in half.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did she get some more caning after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I remember that, honestly. Yes, that's a fact.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about the other teachers, were they also severe?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 One or two of the masters were, yes, but not so severe. Not as severe as the headmaster, but they were severe, although 
they weren't ... the lady teachers I liked better.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you like any of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I liked ... I liked the assistant masters, too. Yes, they were quite a nice bunch, really. The headmaster was the culprit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So it was really the headmaster?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Do you remember if the teachers emphasized the same sort of things as being important, as we mentioned before, such as manners and tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 More so, I think, at Charlotte}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13136618\charrsid1126089 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ville.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about ways of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, oh, yes, certainly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your parents continue to show an interest in your school work there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, they did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did they ever ask you what you did at school, or what you felt about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, oh, yes, they used to ask me, what I felt about it and how I was getting on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did they know about the headmaster and his severity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes. Yes, they would know about it. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 In those days did they visit the school or meet the teachers at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Not that I remember, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about the other children in that school, did they come from similar types of home to your own?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you feel that some of the children had special treatment with the teachers as you had felt in Stoughton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. Oh, definitely so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were the reasons the same, or were they different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think so, certainly in the headmaster's class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And how would he favour a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, he only ... I think ... as far as I can remember, he either liked you or he didn't. If he didn't like you it would show, you see.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did he favour children who came from homes where there was more money or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think money entered into it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Or would it be because they were clever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
This probably, you know, because some people are naturally quicker than others at learning and more alert. He was very alert himself and he expected everybody else to be the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 He was learned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were there any gangs or groups in that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think there were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would they group together for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Well, they used to - pick up their own friends and they'd keep themselves to themselves, you know, and a certain number of people ... and they didn't seem to want to have anything to do with the rest of the class, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would this be because they had the same interests in common?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Or perhaps would it be anything to do with social distinctions, would they feel themselves to be different from some of the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
I think so, yes, partly that, yes. Yes, because at school they came from different homes, you see, and some children's fathers were in a better social position, with a better job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And would there be children at that school who were isolated and seemed alone, left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think there were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Can you remember anyone in particular?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I do remember ... I remember one boy who always seemed to be very sad, you know, and he seeme
d to keep himself quite apart from the other children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When you say 'sad' do you mean he was sad, or you felt sad about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I felt sorry for him myself, but I think he used to look very sad and he seemed to be very sad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I wonder why he was left alone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 He didn't appear to want to mix with anybody, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was there any apparent reason for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I didn't know why ... whether it was anything to do with his home life. But that particular boy, I think he left that sch
ool soon after I did, as a matter of fact, Charlotte}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13136618\charrsid1126089 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ville.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did he have a bad time with punishments, and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think he got punished very much, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Now, let's go on to Holy Trinity School. How old would you have been when you went there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I went to Charlotte}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13136618\charrsid1126089 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ville at 9. Well, I must have been between 10 and 11, when I went to Holy Trinity. I can't remember exactly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would the hours at school be similar, again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. Yes, they were, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And did you go home to lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And this was a Church school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was it mixed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you walk to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, it was quite ... a very short distance, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So it didn't take you very long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, it was going from one side of the road to the other, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about your brothers? and younger sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, my brother, he didn't go to Holy Trinity. I think he had left school then, but he continued at Charlotte}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13136618\charrsid1126089 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ville 'till the time he left, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So were you the only one that made the change?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, my two sisters made the change, my two younger sisters.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was this largely through your influence because you belonged to the choir and you wanted to go to this school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What did you think of Holy Trinity School?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I liked it very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So you were happier there than at the other two?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather, yes. I liked Holy Trinity.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about the teachers do you remember them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 They were very nice, too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was the discipline as strict as Charlotte}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6105815\charrsid1126089 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ville?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
No, no, no. And I think the headmaster was much kinder. As a matter of fact, when I joined Holy Trinity School the headmaster had died a few months before and the new hea
dmaster had not yet arrived, and I remember his coming to Holy Trinity. He was there for a good many ... number of years, too, afterwards. But on the whole the discipline wasn't as strict as at Charlotte}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6105815\charrsid1126089 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ville. But it was very nice, the school was very nice, I enjoyed it very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were the same sort of things emphasized at this school, as at the other 2 schools that we mentioned, like manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Ways of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 All these things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And if you did something that the teachers disapproved of here what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, if they disapproved of anything and you didn't conform, you were then punished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would the punishment be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, you could get the cane, or you would have to stay in and write 1500, or perhaps 500 lines after school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would caning be used much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, not as much as at Charlotte}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6105815\charrsid1126089 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ville, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 It would have to be something more serious, would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about the girls, would they be caned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, occasionally, but not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You can't remember a particular instance where somebody was caned, and what it was for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, if you were talking during class, you see, and the same thing happened a second time, you'd get caned then, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So you'd have one warning, and then the cane?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 One warning, and then you'd be for it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about your parents and your school work here, did they continue to take an interest in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you discuss what you did at school with them? Did they ask you questions about school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would they visit this school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Nor meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did the other children come from similar types of home to your own at Holy Trinity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, some of them did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would it vary? Would there be different groups of children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think so. I don't think that happened here, at Holy Trinity.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were there any gangs or groups in this school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think there were. Not so many, anyway. I don't think it was so prevalent there, as at Charlotte}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6105815\charrsid1126089 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 ville, for instance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Wou
ld there be any difference between the boys and girls in, for instance, class distinctions? Would there be any feeling between them about that, if it was a more mixed school with different social groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't remember there being any class distinction there.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember feeling at a disadvantage, ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no I don't, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what about clever children and not so clever children, would that make any difference as to how much you would be accepted there?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think so. I don't remember it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember any children who were left out there? and seemed very isolated?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, not (}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10515159\charrsid1126089 m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 umble) never, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How old would you be when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 14.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Yes, I would have done, I think, although, of course, in those days money wasn't all that plentiful and of course, we were ... and I was prepared to earn some money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you attend any part time education after you left, such as evening classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I did, yes, for a time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Where was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 At Holy Trinity.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 At Holy Trinity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, they used to have evening classes there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would they be, what subjects would they offer you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, English and shortha
nd. I used to attend the English classes and shorthand classes, and then they closed the night school because they were getting so few people there, and we were transferred to the old Technical School in Park Street, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So the Holy Trinity School ran these evening classes themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, two or 3 schools would give them, Board schools, and so forth, had evening classes, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And then it was gradually taken over by the Technical College?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Well, I suppose we all think at times, after we've left school 'oh, I wish I'd done better at school', you know, and been more studious than we were. I think I have regretted it sometimes and not working hard at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. If I were at school now, today I should work harder, I think, and hope to get a place at a university.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That's what you'd really like to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, certainly. Certainly. I feel sorry for people who haven't been to school, if there are any today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 While you were still at school did you have a part time job or any means of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I did work for a chemist in the High 
Street. Another school friend of mine and I used to work there and we used to deliver medicines and so forth in our spare time, you see, in the afternoons after school and on Saturdays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did you get the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I think the job was advertised and I applied for it and got it. I was there for ... oh, I forget now, quite some time, I think.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What hours did you work? Just in the evening after school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, after school, from about ... I think about half past four 4 o'clock or half past 
4 'till about 6, I think. Half past 5, or 6, I forget exactly, but for an hour or two in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about Sundays, would you work at all on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, not Sundays, no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 But Saturday mornings, yes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Saturdays, yes. Yes, I think quite a few hours on a Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would that be afternoons as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember how much money you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, I don't ... very little, of course, in those days. Well, when I left school I think I was only getting 5 s
hillings a week for a full time job, from about 7 o'clock in the morning 'till 5, half past 5.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Of course, you wouldn't have any holidays with pay at this little job with the chemist, would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember if you felt the money you were given was fair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I suppose in those days we thought it was fair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, when I left school and I think I got 5 shillings, I think I used to give her about 4/6d.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 But when you were doing this little job you'd still give her some?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you give her most of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I think I was getting about half a crown or two shillings then at this chemist's 
shop, I can't quite remember. I gave my mother the lion's share, I'm sure of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What was it spent on? What would she do with it? She would put it into the housekeeping, or would she save it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think she used to put it into the housekeeping money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What did you spend yours on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I suppose sweets, something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You said you did this with another boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have anything to do with the people in the shop? Who worked in the shop, I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, as a ma
tter of fact ... as a matter of fact the name of the chemist was Mr. Tavener, he became mayor of Guildford, and he and his wife ... and they had a son and he's still about, too. And there was another chemist, he used to employ a chemist to help in the sho
p, and the son, he ... his son wasn't a chemist, he didn't work in the shop ... but very nice people, they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you get on well with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I got on very well with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And with the boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And did your employer treat you well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, very well, indeed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So you liked them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did you like the work, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I liked it because when we weren't out delivering medicines we were washing medicine bottles, and so forth. And it wa
s quite interesting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did the job alter your attitude to school in any way, do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Now could you tell me about your first full time job. What was that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 My first full time job? Well, that was at an antique shop in Quarry Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did you get that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That was advertised. At least, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your parents use any influence to help you get it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What exactly did you have to do in that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, the idea wa
s to learn the cabinet making trade, you see. This was antique furniture and all sorts of things; warming pans and brass candle-sticks and all sorts of things in this shop. The workshop was in Mill Lane, and there were 4 men employed there, cabinet makers
 
and polishers, French polishers, and so forth. The idea was, as I say, that I should learn the cabinet making trade, but it was during the 1914 War and I used to spend quite a lot of time at the shop, you know, cleaning up old brass and that sort of thing
,
 and down at the workshop as well. And then some of the men were called up by the Army, you see, and I thought I was being made an errand boy and things didn't seem to me to be any prospect of learning the cabinet making trade because all the staff were g
oing, you see, one by one. So I jumped from the frying pan into the fire and went into the gents' outfitting trade, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Now, before you tell me about that one; going back to the antique shop could you tell me what hours you worked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I started at 7 o'clock in the morning and I left off at, I think, 5 or half past 5.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you work on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no Sundays, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Saturdays? Oh, yes, rather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have a half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Had a half day, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I only worked there for 10 months, so I don't think I had a holiday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see, you didn't qualify?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How much were you paid there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Five shillings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Five shillings a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And did you feel at the time that that was not a fair wage?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, no, I thought it was all right, because in those days we did think that 5/- was quite a lot to start with, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You gave some of this money to your mother, 4/6d. you said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And then you would have the balance of 6d. for yourself, did you still spend it on sweets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think I did, most of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did your employer treat you in this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, very well indeed. It was a lady, as a matter of fact.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And how did you feel about her, did you like her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, she was a very nice person, yes. She was a Roman Catholic as a matter of fact. A very religious person, she was. Very human.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what about the work, did you like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I liked the work, yes, I liked the work really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And then you left after 10 months and you went into the tailoring outfitters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I think that was advertised in the local paper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see, so you got all your jobs through advertisements?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What year would this be? After the War had started, isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I think about ... Let's see, 1915 when I left school ... it was about 1916.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what exactly did you have to do in the tailor's outfitters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, behind the counter, you see, I was an apprentice, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You were serving, were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Serving, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 But were you apprenticed with the idea of eventually doing tailoring yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Not actually tailoring, but o
utfitting. You see, I could've ... there was only bespoke tailoring, they didn't make garments on the premises, you see, they were made at a factory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was the apprenticeship for so long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I wasn't found you see, didn't have to pay a sum of money, but yes, it was supposed to be about 3 years.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What hours did you work there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 From 9 'till ... oh, I think about 7 o'clock. Yes, 9 'till 7.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 On Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, there was no Sunday working. Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Or Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Saturdays, yes. We were late on Saturdays 'till about 8, or half past 7 when we'd knock off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have a half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Half day on Wednesday, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember what you were paid there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't. I can't remember. Probably ... I think it was 7/6 or 10/- a week at the start.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And did you feel satisfied with that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You felt that was fair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, in those days, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What about giving money to your mother, did this continue?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you give her most of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I used to give her most of it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 But you had a little left to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what had you used to spend it on now, that you had a little more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I used to put some away for clothes, you know, and my mother did, too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you clothe yourself now, or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I couldn't clothe myself in those days, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So she'd still have to help you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And you were living at home, so would you pay towards your board?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did you get on with the other people you worked with there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Very well, as a matter of fact, because there was only the manager and myself there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What was he like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Very nice man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You got on well with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I got on well with him, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what about the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Yes, I liked the work. But unfortunately, the job didn't last too long there because the manager was called up to join the Army and ... John Riggs was the
 name of the firm - and Mr. Riggs decided to close down rather than get another manager in, because ... very difficult in the war days. So we closed down and I had to get another job, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So what happened to you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So I went to another job in the town, in the same line.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Outfitters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Outfitters, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And this would be before the end of 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes. This would be about ... now let's see ... about 1917, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How long would you be there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 At this other job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, some years, until about ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I see, that would be the last one before the end of the War, before the end of 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. I was there until about 19--, oh, the early '20's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did you get that, through recommendations from your ... the shop you worked for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I believe I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What did you have to do in that job, was it the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 The same, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were the hours the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Longer even because sometimes on a Saturday night we got finished at half passed nine or quarter to ten. On a Saturday night, yes, yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you still have a half day?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, half day, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was the pay the same or would it be different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, pay was better. The pay was better, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You don't remember what it was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Do you remember what you felt about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 About the pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you feel it was fair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, after a time I didn't because it was very hard work. We were understaffed, as a m
atter of fact, and very tiring, especially on a Saturday on your feet all day and tired out, and ... no, the pay wasn't as much as it should have been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you still give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And would she spend it on the same things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Yes, well, as a matter of fact by then I was more or less able to clothe myself, you see, and we used to get our clothes ... that was one thing about it ... at cost price, you see, so that was one compensation, you s
ee, for having a low salary, you see. That was a big saving, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And your mother would use the money that you gave her in the housekeeping, would she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did you get on with the other people in that business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, very well. Very well indeed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What was your employer like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, he was very easy to get on with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you like him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 How did you feel about the work? It was hard you said, but did you like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, to a certain extent, but i
n time I got rather tired there, you see. I'll tell you, it must have been ... let me see, about 1924 ... I stayed there 'till about 1924, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What did you do after that, before you became a verger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I went, in 1924, to a small tailor and ou
tfitter in the town. As a matter of fact this man, I knew him, knew his sons very well, and this poor man was very ill and he was single-handed and I knew he wanted somebody and he'd got a son, his own son was in the trade but away from Guildford, you see
.
 And this man's daughter, I met her one day and she was speaking about her father and she said he was looking for somebody to help in the shop because he was ill, you see, and single-handed, he was only just about able to get about, and offered me a job, 
y
ou see, said 'come and see my father'. I did, I went and saw him and I decided I wanted the job, he offered me the job, you see, and I stayed there for about 2 or 3 years. As a matter of fact after a few months the old chap, he became ... he had to take t
o him bed and he died. And then his son left his job, a similar job, and came to Guildford and carried on, you see, and managed the business.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What happened to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I carried on with him for some time, and this young man, he'd got a brother
 in the same trade in a wholesale business in London, you see, and he wanted to get him into it in the shop. There wasn't enough money coming in, you see, to employ him and me so I had to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And what did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I got a job in the bo
rough surveyor's office, as a matter of fact and I was there for about ... just about 3 years before I took on the job as verger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What actually did you do in the borough surveyor's office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, my chief work was printing and developing blueprin
ts, plans and so forth in this big printing machine, and I used to go out, too, as a matter of fact, on surveying jobs, you know. I went with one of the assistants to survey and take the levels for the by-pass, which was nearly 40 years ago ... 37 years a
go, we started the job, from Boxgrove Road, Stoke Park to Onslow Village. It was a nice job, too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You liked it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I liked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you have preferred any other type of occupation? You had the antique, tailoring and surveying.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, the job I liked best was my last job, verger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you like to have gone on with that if you hadn't become a verger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I would have gone on ... I would still have been at the borough surveyor's, I suppose. I could have done, you see, could have 
stayed on, but this job was offered me and I was already interested in Church work and I liked the job, you see, so I took it on and stayed 36 and three-quarter years on it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So your apprenticeship was really in the tailoring one, wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Not in any of the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you belong to any trade union or professional organization?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I didn't, no, no. As a matter of fact I did join the Shop Assistants' Union when I was in the first outfitting job, that was throu
gh the influence of the manager, but after a time I came out of it because in those days, you know, a good many employers looked rather disdainfully on the trade unions, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes. And I was told, too, that some employers would 
not employ a trade unionist, you see. So I thought I'd better come out, but I had an awful job to get out of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 They didn't want you to come out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, my word, no. I had an awful job to get out of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests, or different ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, I think they had varied interests, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You felt they were different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you feel there were divisions of interest among the workers, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, yes, I'm sure there were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers, did you feel that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I didn't notice that particularly, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, of course, you've got ... when you start full time work you've got a deeper sense of responsibility, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When you're earning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When you're earning, oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And of course, you were helping your family, too, weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Now, may I ask you a few questions about your life at home after you left school. You continued to live at home until you }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15143913 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 , did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you spend your Sunday any differently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I used to ... I always went to Church 2 or 3 times on a Sunday and I still continue to do so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, not a great interest, no. A certain amount of interest, but not ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would your views be at this stage of your life? After you'd left school and were starting work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 My political views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I worked with Conservatives quite a bit, you know, and I think they probably influenced me a bit, you see, in their way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You mean people who'd worked in households, big households?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. And people I worked with were Conservatives, and some workmen I worked with, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 In your jobs, were you thinking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So you think this influenced you, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So your views would be Conservative at that stage in your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you vote in a general election before 1919? When would you be 21?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 I was {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname metricconverter}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue 21 in}}}21 in
{\*\xmlclose} 1922. No, no. The age is 21, isn't it, or was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes. So you didn't vote in an election. Did you ever feel under any pressure from anybody to vote for a pa
rticular party? such as your employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Were you ever a member of the Conservative Party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you ever work for one of the parties at an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Or did you take part in any political activity other than at election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
You told me earlier something of how you spent your spare time when you were at school; now you were working full time did you use your spare time in the same way or did you do different things?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 When I was working? There was only work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 You were still in the choir at the Church were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
That's right. Well, no, my voice broke at the age of ... let me see, now, 14 or 15. I naturally, had to leave the choir, but I was a server, an altar server. I became an altar server in 1914, and I used to serve in week times as well as on Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And you belonged to that group of servers you said, didn't you? There was a little association of servers wasn't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, that's right? (name of group) San}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10515159\charrsid1126089 c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 tuary, yes. Well, sometimes I have served as much as six times in a week in years gone by. But when my voice settled down I went back in the choir to sing bass, you see, for some years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So you were only out of the choir for a year or two?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 A short time, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you do anything else, apart from the choir, now? And the serving in Church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
No, I joined ... I was still a member of the Guild, Communicants' Guild. I used to go to their social gatherings, you know. We used to have a club and we used to meet about once or twice a week, at the Church hall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So, you'd go out in the evenings, sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Would you go anywhere else, but to one of the Church clubs or activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 To the pictures occasionally, or sometimes to the theatre if there was anything good, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Who would you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Probably with my sister ... one of my sisters, or my brother. Now, what year are we speaking of? After I left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, you'd left school. You're in the period, really, after you'd left school 'till the end of 1918, the period we're thinking about.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, I used to go to the pictures occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you make any new friends, boys or girls, at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 No, I don't think ... I don't know whether I met any ... m
y old school friends, I think I still associated with them, and a friend of mine who is now Roman Catholic, an old choir boy friend of mine, I still continued to meet him, you know, quite frequently.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you ever take friends home in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, rather, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have any special friends at that time? Did you have a special boy friend or a special girl friend?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, this special boy friends, this chappie who's now a Roman Catholic, yes, I used to ... I think he was my ... i
n those days, my greatest boyfriend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 What would you do with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 
Well, we used to go out quite frequently, you know, go for long walks, and he used to come ... he'd come to my house and I'd go to his house, you see. And I was just wondering when I ... I met my wife about that time, 1919.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Was she a Guildford girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, lived quite near.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did your parents meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, oh, yes, rather, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did they expect to know where you were when you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I think I used to tell them, used to say where I was going, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did you have to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes, oh, yes, rather, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Even when you were working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes, I never ... I wasn't expected to stay too late. Used to be home by 10. Oh, yes, rather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did that apply to all the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes. Yes, rather, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 And, if you had met your wife about this time, where would you go with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Well, I used to go to her house, and that, and she'd come to my h
ouse. We'd go to the pictures sometimes, or go to a theatre, go for walks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Did she belong to Holy Trinity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9459843 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 So she'd be involved in some of the activities that you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12659671 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13126736\charrsid1126089 Yes.
